Title: Framework agreement procedure first stage
Description: This contracting process follows on from the related process to establish a framework. The suppliers on the framework are listed in the award section of the related process.

Title: Planning process
Description: This contracting process follows on from the related planning process.

Title: Parent contract (for sub-contracts)
Description: This contracting process may result in a sub-contract of the related process.

Title: Prior process
Description: This contracting process is the renewal or replacement of the related prior process.

Title: Unsuccessful process
Description: This contracting process follows on from an previous unsuccessful process.

Title: Sub-contract
Description: The related process may result in a sub-contract of this contract.

Title: Replacement process
Description: The related process may result in the replacement of this contract.

Title: Renewal process
Description: The related process may result in the renewal of this contract.
